                  <div class=""> 
                    <p class="form_caption"></p><h1>
	<strong><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: inherit;">CANCELLATION, RETURN AND SHIPPING</span></strong></h1>
<h1>
	<u style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;"><span style=" "><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">Pricing Policy</span></strong></span></u></h1>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">Prices on the website are subject to change, as received from manufacturer(s), without any prior notice and updated on this website regularly. However, once order is complete, customer is charged the applicable amount that appears at the time of completion of order. &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;vertical-align:top;">
	<u><span style=" "><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">Cancellation Policy</span></strong></span></u></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">An order cannot be edited or changed, once an order is complete and the order ID is generated. But an order can be canceled at any time before the payment is processed. To cancel an order, a customer is required to CONTACT US.&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">If an order is cancelled before payment has been processed, there are no charges.&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">Once the&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">order has been released for processing<span style="border:none windowtext 1.0pt;padding:0in;">&nbsp;or payment is made, a customer is liable to pay 15% restocking fee calculated on the amount of the order and the remaining amount is credited back. We do not entertain cash refunds.</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;vertical-align:top;">
	<u><span style=" "><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">Return &amp; Refund Policy</span></strong></span></u></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">Customer is eligible to return an order without incurring any charges if it doesn’t contain what was ordered or it was damaged when delivered. Otherwise, customer is liable to pay 15% restocking fee calculated on the amount of the order for the return of order.</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:22.5pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">Once an order has been returned, we will refund the amount back to customer store credit after deducting the applicable necessary charges.</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">At the time of delivery, inspect your package from outside. If the package is damaged on the outside, do not accept the package and do not sign the delivery slip. Simply return the damaged package. Signing of the delivery slip is taken as your consent that the package has not been damaged in transit.</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">After opening the package, if you find that the contents of your received order are damaged from inside or are different from what you ordered, lodge your complaint within 24 hours of receipt of your order at CONTACT US.&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">We try our best to resolve your complaint within 24 – 48 working hours. However, the resolution time may vary depending on the nature of the complaint.</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">We will initiate and launch an internal investigation and the report of that investigation would be shared with you as full and final resolution of your complaint.&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">If you are found eligible for return/refund of the ordered products in full or part thereof, then we will process the same under intimation to you.</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">Cold chain order cannot be cancelled, once it has been shipped. Cold chain order cannot be returned and does not qualify for refund. However, in case the received cold chain product is different from what you ordered, we will reship the correct order to you.</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;vertical-align:top;">
	<u><span style=" "><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">Shipping Policy</span></strong></span></u></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">We deliver our products anywhere in Pakistan provided we have a correct address. We do not ship to P.O. Boxes, as there will be no one available to sign the delivery note.</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">We deliver temperature sensitive orders in over 175 cities across Pakistan. We take special precautionary steps from the time we receive a product from the manufacturer till the time of its delivery to the customer to ensure that its condition and temperature is maintained as recommended by the manufacturer. Special packing material and gel pouches are used to maintain the temperature even during delivery. &nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; background: white; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; background: white; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">A customer is eligible to place an order from outside Pakistan as long as the delivery address is in Pakistan. Customer can add multiple addresses to an existing account on our website and check the desired address in Pakistan for delivery of a particular order.</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">We deliver through leading courier and logistics companies. The products are packaged in secure and safe boxes. An invoice of the order is included inside the package which is delivered within the stipulated time period of relevant courier company. Once an order is</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black;">&nbsp;dispatched, customer is provided with tracking number to trace the order.</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">Our delivery charges are very competitive and vary from city to city. Applicable delivery charges are shown at the time of booking an order.&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;vertical-align:top;">
	<span style=" "><span style="font-size: 16px; color: black; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;">We also provide free delivery for certain qualifying orders on the basis of prevalent policy barring any cold chain order.</span></span></p>
<p></p>
